				<h1>Welcome to Rent Review Services</h1>
				<h2>Are you looking for expert advice on a potential review <br/>of your rent?</h2>
				<p>We specialise in negotiating rent reviews and lease renewal terms on shops,
				offices, restaurants, and industrial premises in the Greater London area. We 
				also carry out formal commercial valuations, rate appeals, management, sales 
				and lettings.</p>
				<h2>Why use Rent Review Services?</h2>
				<ol>
					<li>We are a department of a firm of Charterd Surveyors, offering focused <br/>professional advice.</li>
					<li>The partners have experience in this type of work since 1968</li>
					<li>We guarantee that your case will be handled promptly, courteously and <br/>efficiently by a partner</li>
					<li>We have detailed knowledge of current market trends and rental values.</li>
					<li>We thoroughly look at every aspect of your case including the lease terms, comparable rental 
					evidence, validity of notices, effects of improvements and service charges etc.</li>
					<li>If necessary we will present your case at Arbitration or Court.</li>
					<li>We have a very broad client list, including: Urbium plc, Soho Bars, Scotch Steak House Group, 
					Stoneguard, JCDecaux, Tile Depot, Supersave, Food City, City Screen, Herbmedic etc., and act for 
					numerous loyal small independent traders.</li>
				</ol>	
